  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 160°C (320°F).",
    "Slice bell peppers and onions, then dice garlic cloves.",
    "Place corned beef in a baking dish. Add sliced bell peppers and chopped onions over it.",
    "Drizzle tomato paste on top of the vegetables and sprinkle with salt and pepper.",
    "Roast for 35 minutes at 160°C (320°F).",
    "Meanwhile, heat olive oil in a wok or large skillet. Add minced garlic and sauté until fragrant.",
    "Add roasted corned beef mixture to the wok and stir-fry for another 10-15 minutes or until heated through.",
    "Season with salt and pepper as desired.",
    "Serve hot as a main dish."
  ],
